---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ButtonLink from '../../components/ui/ButtonLink.astro';
import SimpleCard from '../../components/cards/SimpleCard.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Teaching"
  description="Open teaching resources and learning paths for biological software engineering."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950">Teaching</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
      DRAGGON Lab teaching aims to prepare students to become biological software engineers:
      researchers who connect biology, computation, engineering, standards, data, automation, and
      responsible design.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-slate-600">
      Project-based learning is central. Students should design genetic systems, analyze biological
      data, build computational workflows, document reusable tools, and communicate results clearly.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <SimpleCard title="Foundations"
        >Foundational concepts for biology, computation, standards, and workflows.</SimpleCard
      >
      <SimpleCard title="Computer-Aided BioDesign"
        >Design and automate biological engineering workflows.</SimpleCard
      >
      <SimpleCard title="AI in Computational Biology"
        >Use machine learning with biological data and design problems.</SimpleCard
      >
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-violet-100 bg-white p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Open teaching resources</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">
        Unless otherwise noted, DRAGGON Lab teaching materials are shared for reuse with attribution
        under the site content license.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">
        If you have teaching materials, notebooks, examples, diagrams, or workshop ideas that fit
        DRAGGON Lab themes, you are welcome to suggest them through GitHub or contact the lab.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <ButtonLink
          href="https://github.com/DRAGGON-Lab/draggon-lab.github.io/issues/new?template=teaching-resource-request.yml"
          >Suggest a resource</ButtonLink
        ><ButtonLink href="mailto:contact@draggonlab.org" variant="secondary"
          >Contact DRAGGON Lab</ButtonLink
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
